inputs: [['From its invitingly upbeat overture to its pathos-filled but ultimately life-affirming finale , Martin is a masterfully conducted work .', 'Its engaging simplicity is driven by appealing leads .', 'It has more in common with a fireworks display than a movie , which normally is expected to have characters and a storyline .', 'The big-screen Scooby makes the silly original cartoon seem smart and well-crafted in comparison .', 'Take nothing seriously and enjoy the ride .', "With Zoe Clarke-Williams 's lackluster thriller `` New Best Friend '' , who needs enemies ?", 'The moral shrapnel and mental shellshock will linger long after this film has ended .', 'I have always appreciated a smartly written motion picture , and , whatever flaws Igby Goes Down may possess , it is undeniably that .', 'Captivates and shows how a skillful filmmaker can impart a message without bludgeoning the audience over the head .', "Swimming is above all about a young woman 's face , and by casting an actress whose face projects that woman 's doubts and yearnings , it succeeds .", "It 's hard to say who might enjoy this , are there Tolstoy groupies out there ?", "The movie is as padded as Allen 's jelly belly .", "I did n't smile .", "Uzumaki 's interesting social parallel and defiant aesthetic seems a prostituted muse ...", 'The art direction is often exquisite , and the anthropomorphic animal characters are beautifully realized through clever makeup design , leaving one to hope that the eventual DVD release will offer subtitles and the original Italian-language soundtrack .', "As action-adventure , this space-based homage to Robert Louis Stevenson 's Treasure Island fires on all plasma conduits .", 'Watching this gentle , mesmerizing portrait of a man coming to terms with time , you barely realize your mind is being blown .', 'The film is strictly routine .', 'Despite its faults , Gangs excels in spectacle and pacing .', "Even as it pays earnest homage to turntablists and beat jugglers , old schoolers and current innovators , Scratch is great fun , full of the kind of energy it 's documenting ."], ['From its invitingly upbeat overture to its pathos-filled but ultimately life-affirming finale , Martin is a masterfully conducted work .', 'Its engaging simplicity is driven by appealing leads .', 'It has more in common with a fireworks display than a movie , which normally is expected to have characters and a storyline .', 'The big-screen Scooby makes the silly original cartoon seem smart and well-crafted in comparison .', 'Take nothing seriously and enjoy the ride .', "With Zoe Clarke-Williams 's lackluster thriller `` New Best Friend '' , who needs enemies ?", 'The moral shrapnel and mental shellshock will linger long after this film has ended .', 'I have always appreciated a smartly written motion picture , and , whatever flaws Igby Goes Down may possess , it is undeniably that .', 'Captivates and shows how a skillful filmmaker can impart a message without bludgeoning the audience over the head .', "Swimming is above all about a young woman 's face , and by casting an actress whose face projects that woman 's doubts and yearnings , it succeeds .", "It 's hard to say who might enjoy this , are there Tolstoy groupies out there ?", "The movie is as padded as Allen 's jelly belly .", "I did n't smile .", "Uzumaki 's interesting social parallel and defiant aesthetic seems a prostituted muse ...", 'The art direction is often exquisite , and the anthropomorphic animal characters are beautifully realized
